{"title":"雪松","date":"2021-03-25T11:00:57.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 25, 2021","L":"03/25/2021","MM-DD":"03-25"},"author":"白桦","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/sunrise-4698807_1280.webp","link":"2021/03/25/Cedar","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2021-03-25T11:04:54.643Z","content":"<p>从来都不合时宜地<br>\n在这春天<br>\n想起那棵雪松</p>\n<p>挺拔而茂盛<br>\n不信天命地<br>\n郁郁葱葱</p>\n<p>再烈的风也带不走<br>\n只空留枝桠上<br>\n咸涩的糖霜</p>\n<p>人心尚无<br>\n树心层层<br>\n春天，见不得<br>\n风去叶落</p>\n","prev":{"title":"新月","link":"2021/04/22/Crescent"},"next":{"title":"7PM","link":"2021/03/16/7PM"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2021/03/25/Cedar/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"March 25, 2021"},"reading_time":"68 words in 1 min"}